Win32-Filenames

This module has no dependencies outside of the base perl modules.

With this module, you can easily validate if a filename is a valid 
windows filename. It can also be used to convert an invalid filename into a 
valid filename.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


